snippet.title: No Man's Sky Worlds Part I Update Trailer
snippet.description:
The latest free update to No Man's Sky, Worlds Part I (version 5.0), ushers in an entire universe refresh, bringing huge leaps in water and cloud quality, as well as increased planetary variety, new gameplay features, and more!

Full patch notes available here: https://www.nomanssky.com/worlds-part-I-update
